# BDD

BDD - Behaviour Driven Development
[Cucumber](https://cucumber.io/) - the company 
Gerkhins - the syntax, a specialized DSL that expresses the tests in a read-able format. Different languages and frameworks have different implementations
[Cucumber.js](https://cucumber.io/docs/installation/javascript/) - the tool as a package that interpret Gerkhins sysntax and integrates with js.
Specflow - the.NET implementation
